    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Entrance doorbell devices activated by turning a bar or thumb piece located on the outside of an exterior door frame that communicates with a bell located somewhere inside the door frame.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
